{"tid":765132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我的少女時代女主角曾揚最喜愛的國家是台灣 被大陸網友發現後即發愛國宣言","createTime":"2018-08-02T13:50:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T15:07:19.000Z","uid":67294,"like":19,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"de510490905caa7dbf7fdc95dfa88a0cd0a9d24b","tid":765132,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T13:50:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/x4Pl4Jnv8gLgCsy0As1ihg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/newtalk.tw/a5180e526d034ecba51f1b2aadf98a86\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fx4Pl4Jnv8gLgCsy0As1ihg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fa5180e526d034ecba51f1b2aadf98a86&h=1455f521&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又有台灣藝人到對岸發展，但因公開發言被中國網友認定「涉獨」而遭到圍剿了！這次引發抗議風波的是以《等一個人咖啡》和《我的少女時代》兩片走紅的影星宋芸樺，「罪證」則是3年前的一段採訪視頻。當時她提到「最喜歡的國家是台灣」，被網友質疑「什麼時候台灣變成國家了？」，「希望小姊姊長點心吧！」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>宋芸樺主演的《西虹市首富》目前正在中國熱映中，今天票房已超過14億</strong>。有網友到其官微置頂微博下留言表示，「好後悔去看，因為女主是台獨」。根據中國媒體環球網下午的最新報導，網友芸芸眾口已經把宋芸樺的名字迅速推上微博熱搜。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日個女主角微博<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/02/215017_4d81ebbc05bfe160e31a3855cf005acb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F02%2F215017_4d81ebbc05bfe160e31a3855cf005acb.jpg&h=d915d422&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好撚肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c2749f2974b1dc7e2223e00836931f721b0a570","tid":765132,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T13:52:50.000Z","msg":"補鑊想奶共就打埋殘體啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b36f5dd9e9bef4f625c